{
  "version": "1",
  "slug": "gitlab",
  "kind": "compose",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "GitLab",
    "description": "A **complete DevOps platform** that provides Git repository management, CI/CD pipelines,\nissue tracking, and container registry in a single application.\n## Prerequisites\n- ...\n**Performance Presets**:\n- `homelab`: Optimized for low-resource environments (limited workers, reduced PostgreSQL buffers)\n- `default`: Standard server configuration for production use\n**External URL**:\n- Set to your public domain (e.g., `https://gitlab.example.com`) for proper clone URLs\n- Affects SSH clone URLs and web links in emails/notifications\n**Container Registry**:\n- Enable if you need private Docker image hosting\n- Requires separate external URL (e.g., `https://registry.example.com`)\n## Resources\n- **Project**: https://about.gitlab.com/\n- **Documentation**: https://docs.gitlab.com/\n- **Community**: https://forum.gitlab.com/",
    "tags": [
      "traefik"
    ],
    "author": "Christian Lempa",
    "template_version": "18.8.4-ce.0",
    "icon": {
      "provider": "simple-icons",
      "id": "gitlab"
    },
    "date": "2026-02-10",
    "next_steps": "## Post-Installation Steps\n1. **Start GitLab**:\n  ```bash\n  docker compose up -d\n  ```\n2. **Wait for\\\n  \\ initialization** (2-5 minutes):\n    ```bash\n    docker compose logs -f gitlab\n    ```\n    Wait for message: `gitlab\\\n  \\ Reconfigured!`\n  3. **Access the web interface**:\n    {% if traefik_enabled -%}\n    - Via Traefik: https://{{ traefik_host\\\n  \\ }}\n    {% if not traefik_enabled and network_mode == 'bridge' %}- Direct access: http://localhost:{{ ports_http }}{%\\\n  \\ endif %}\n    {%- else -%}\n    - Open {{ external_url }} in your browser\n    {% if network_mode == 'bridge' %}- Or: http://localhost:{{\\\n  \\ ports_http }}{% endif %}\n    {%- endif %}\n  4. **Initial login credentials**:\n    - **Username**: `root`\n    - **Password**:\\\n  \\ `{{ root_password }}`\n    > **Important**: This password only works on FIRST initialization.\n    > Change it immediately\\\n  \\ after first login via GitLab's web interface!\n  5. **Configure SSH** (optional):\n    - SSH clone URLs will use port `{{\\\n  \\ ports_ssh }}`\n    - Update your Git remote if needed\n  ## Additional Resources\n  - Documentation: https://docs.gitlab.com/\n  \\\n  - GitLab Runner: https://docs.gitlab.com/runner/"
  },
  "entrypoint": {
    "path": "compose.yaml",
    "type": "file"
  },
  "variables": [
    {
      "key": "general",
      "title": "General",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "service_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Docker service name",
          "required": false,
          "default": "gitlab",
          "description": "Docker service name"
        },
        {
          "name": "external_url",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "External URL for GitLab",
          "required": false,
          "default": "http://localhost",
          "description": "External URL for GitLab"
        },
        {
          "name": "root_email",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Initial root user email address",
          "required": false,
          "default": "admin@example.com",
          "description": "Initial root user email address"
        },
        {
          "name": "root_password",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Initial root user password (only used on first initialization)",
          "required": false,
          "description": "Initial root user password (only used on first initialization)",
          "sensitive": true,
          "autogenerated": true
        },
        {
          "name": "default_theme",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "Default GitLab UI theme (2 = dark mode)",
          "required": false,
          "default": 2,
          "description": "Default GitLab UI theme (2 = dark mode)"
        },
        {
          "name": "default_color_mode",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "Default color mode (2 = dark mode)",
          "required": false,
          "default": 2,
          "description": "Default color mode (2 = dark mode)"
        },
        {
          "name": "disable_usage_data",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Disable product usage metrics upload to GitLab",
          "required": false,
          "default": true,
          "description": "Disable product usage metrics upload to GitLab"
        },
        {
          "name": "restart_policy",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Restart Policy",
          "required": true,
          "default": "unless-stopped",
          "options": [
            "unless-stopped",
            "always",
            "on-failure",
            "no"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "advanced",
      "title": "Advanced Settings",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "performance_preset",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Performance optimization profile",
          "required": false,
          "default": "homelab",
          "description": "Performance optimization profile",
          "options": [
            "homelab",
            "default"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "prometheus_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Prometheus monitoring",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Prometheus monitoring"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "ports",
      "title": "Ports",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "ports_http",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Ports Http",
          "required": false,
          "default": 80
        },
        {
          "name": "ports_ssh",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Ports Ssh",
          "required": false,
          "default": 2424
        },
        {
          "name": "ports_registry",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "Container Registry port",
          "required": false,
          "default": 5000,
          "description": "Container Registry port"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "registry",
      "title": "Registry",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "registry_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable GitLab Container Registry",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable GitLab Container Registry"
        },
        {
          "name": "registry_external_url",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "External URL for Container Registry",
          "required": false,
          "default": "http://localhost:5000",
          "description": "External URL for Container Registry"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "traefik",
      "title": "Traefik",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "traefik_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Host",
          "required": false,
          "default": "gitlab.home.arpa"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_registry_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Hostname for Container Registry in Traefik (if enabled)",
          "required": false,
          "default": "registry.home.arpa",
          "description": "Hostname for Container Registry in Traefik (if enabled)",
          "needs": [
            "registry_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_network",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Network",
          "required": true,
          "default": "traefik"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_domain",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Domain",
          "required": true,
          "default": "home.arpa"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Traefik integration",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Traefik integration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "traefik-tls",
      "title": "Traefik TLS",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_certresolver",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Traefik Tls Certresolver",
          "required": true,
          "default": "cloudflare"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Traefik TLS",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Traefik TLS"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "email",
      "title": "Email",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "email_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable email server configuration",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable email server configuration"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "SMTP server hostname",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "SMTP server hostname"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_port",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "SMTP server port",
          "required": false,
          "default": 587,
          "description": "SMTP server port"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_username",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "SMTP username",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "SMTP username"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_password",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "SMTP password",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "SMTP password",
          "sensitive": true
        },
        {
          "name": "email_from",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "From email address",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "From email address"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_use_tls",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Use TLS encryption",
          "required": false,
          "default": true,
          "description": "Use TLS encryption"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_use_ssl",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Use SSL encryption",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Use SSL encryption"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "authentik",
      "title": "Authentik",
      "variables": [
        {
          "name": "authentik_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Enable Authentik SSO integration",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Authentik SSO integration"
        },
        {
          "name": "authentik_url",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Authentik base URL (e.g., https://auth.example.com)",
          "required": false,
          "default": "https://auth.home.arpa",
          "description": "Authentik base URL (e.g., https://auth.example.com)"
        },
        {
          "name": "authentik_slug",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Authentik application slug",
          "required": false,
          "default": "gitlab",
          "description": "Authentik application slug"
        },
        {
          "name": "authentik_client_id",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "OAuth client ID from Authentik provider",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "OAuth client ID from Authentik provider"
        },
        {
          "name": "authentik_client_secret",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "OAuth client secret from Authentik provider",
          "required": false,
          "default": "",
          "description": "OAuth client secret from Authentik provider",
          "sensitive": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "legacy": {
    "schema": "1.2"
  }
}
